Author: Lucas VHH Tran [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Lucas VHH Tran <lucas.tran@ck-care.ch>
Description: Provides high-quality, publication-ready visualizations for 
    clinical and multi-omics data analysis. Built on ggplot2, the package 
    offers specialized plot types including forest plots, volcano plots, 
    Kaplan-Meier survival curves, waterfall plots, swimmer plots, heatmaps,
    PCA/MDS plots, and many more. Features automatic legends, faceting, 
    journal-specific themes (Nature, Science, NEJM, etc.), and statistical 
    annotations for seamless integration into scientific publications.
